   /*
 * Load useful variables
 */
var imgDB = new Array();
var imgDBb = new Array();
var userDB = new Array();

var slideDBT = new Array();
var slideDBB = new Array();

var topMax,topMin,topIndex;
var bottomMax,bottomMin,bottomIndex;

var screen_width,screen_height,idimx,idimy,ipad;

var ULX,ULY,ULXX,ULYY;
var URX,URY,URXX,URYY;
var LLX,LLY,LLXX,LLYY;
var LRX,LRY,LRXX,LRYY;

/*
 * Get Image from image array db
 */
function getImg(id) {
	return newImg(imgDB[id]);
}

/*
 * Get random image from imgDB
 */
function getRandImg() {
	var i = rand(imgDB.length);
	return getImg(i);
}

//-------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Bottoms

/*
 * Get Image from image array db
 */
function getImgBottoms(id) {
	return newImg(imgDBb[id]);
}

/*
 * Get random image from imgDB
 */
function getRandImgBottoms() {
	var i = rand(imgDBb.length);
	return getImgBottoms(i);
}

//-------------------------------------------------------------------------

/*
 * Get user name
 */
function userName(id) {
	return userDB[id]["id"];
}

/*
 * Initialize sliding arrays
 */
function initSlider() {
	topMin = bottomMin = topIndex = bottomIndex = 0;
	topMax = bottomMax = 10;
	topMax--;
	bottomMax--;
	
	//var topVals = genUniqueSlider(topMax);
	//var botVals = genUniqueSlider(bottomMax);
	
	for(i=0;i&lt;topMax;i++) {
		slideDBT[i] = i;//imgDB[i].get_id();//topVals[i];
	}
	
	for(j=0;j&lt;bottomMax;j++) {
		slideDBB[j] = j;//imgDBb[j].get_id();//botVals[j];
	}
}

/*
 * Unique slider values, prevent duplicates
 */
function genUniqueSlider(size) {
	var maximus = size;
	var values = new Array();

	for(i=0;i&lt;maximus;i++) { // Loop through array
		var n = rand(maximus);
		var original = true;
		
		for(j=0;j&lt;maximus;j++) { // Search for existing original
			if(values[j] == n)
				original = false;
		}
		
		if(original)
			values.push(n);
		else
			i--;
	}
	
	return values;
}

	imgDB = createImageArray(topsA); // Load images
	imgDBb = createImageArray(bottomsA);
	
	initSlider();
}

/*
 * Create js image array
 */
function createImageArray(arr) {
	var imgAr = new Array();
	
	for(i=0;i&lt;arr.length;i++) {
		imgAr[i] = new MACImage();
		imgAr[i].id = arr[i]["id"];
		//var str = arr[i]["data"];
		//str = str.replace(/\//gi, ""); // Remove forward slashes (windows)
		imgAr[i].data = arr[i]["data"];//str.replace(/\\/gi, "");  // Rmoves back slashes
        imgAr[i].pid = arr[i]["poster_id"];
	}
	return imgAr;
}

     <script>
      &lt;!--INITIALIZE--&gt;
		init();
     </script>
     <table border="0">
      <tr>
       <td>
        <script>
         /*
			 * Translator methods
			 */
			function translateDown() { // Right
				bottomIndex++;
				if(bottomIndex &gt;= bottomMax) {
					bottomIndex = bottomMin;
				}
			}
			function translateUp() { // Left
				bottomIndex--;
				if(bottomIndex &lt; bottomMin) {
					bottomIndex = bottomMax-1;
				}
			}
			function translateRight() {
				topIndex++;
				if(topIndex &gt;= topMax) {
					topIndex = topMin;
				}
			}
			function translateLeft() {
				topIndex--;
				if(topIndex &lt; topMin) {
					topIndex = topMax-1;
				}
			}
			
			function resetLottery() {
				var img = document.getElementById("match");
				if(img)
					img.src = "recognize.jpg";
			}
			
			function topI() {
				return slideDBT[topIndex];
			}
			function botI() {
				return slideDBB[bottomIndex];
			}
			function lottery() {
				var a = imgDB[topI()].get_pid();//userName(topI());
				var b = imgDBb[botI()].get_pid();//userName(botI());
				
				//alert("a:"+a+",b:"+b);
				
				if(a==b) {
					document.getElementById("match").src = "match.jpg";
				} else {
					document.getElementById("match").src = "wrong.jpg";
				}
				setTimeout(resetLottery,2500);
			}
        </script>
       </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
       <td>
        <canvas height="450" id="canvasing" width="900">
        </canvas>
        <script>
         /*
		 * Rendering methods
		 */
		var frame=0;
		function drawText(msg,x,y) {
			var c=document.getElementById("canvasing");
            var ct=c.getContext("2d");
			
			ct.font="12pt Verdana";
			ct.fillStyle="black";
			ct.fillText(msg,x,y);
		}
		
		function drawImg(img,x,y,frame) {
			var c=document.getElementById("canvasing");
            var ct=c.getContext("2d");
			ct.fillStyle="#000000";
			if(frame) {
				ct.globalAlpha = 0.6;
				if(!img.complete)
					ct.fillRect(x+(ipad*1.5),y+ipad,idimx-(ipad*3),idimy-(ipad*2));
				else
					ct.drawImage(img,x+(ipad*1.5),y+ipad,idimx-(ipad*3),idimy-(ipad*2));
			} else {
				ct.globalAlpha = 1.0;
				if(!img.complete)
					ct.fillRect(x,y,idimx,idimy);
				else
					ct.drawImage(img,x,y,idimx,idimy);
			}
			ct.globalAlpha = 1.0;
		}
		
		function clearCanvas() {
			var c=document.getElementById("canvasing");
            var ct=c.getContext("2d");
            ct.fillStyle="white";
            ct.fillRect(0,0,screen_width,screen_height);
		}
		
		function drawImgIndex() {
			var y1 = 30;
			var y2 = 10;
			;
			translateLeft();
				var imga = getImg(topI());
			translateRight();
				var imgb = getImg(topI());
			translateRight();
				var imgc = getImg(topI());
			translateLeft();
			;
			var y = y1+idimy+5;
			var yy = ipad+30;
			;
			translateUp();
				var imgd = getImgBottoms(botI());
			translateDown();
				var imge = getImgBottoms(botI());
			translateDown();
				var imgf = getImgBottoms(botI());
			translateUp();
			;
			;
			drawImg(imga,0,y1+y2,true);
			drawImg(imgb,idimx,y1,false);
			drawImg(imgc,idimx+idimx,y1+y2,true);
			;
			drawImg(imgd,0,y-yy,true);
			drawImg(imge,idimx,y,false);
			drawImg(imgf,idimx+idimx,y-yy,true);
		}
		
		function rendering() {
			clearCanvas();
			var verbose = false;
			if(verbose) {
				drawText("frame: "+frame,2,20);
				drawText("T: "+topIndex+", ImgI: "+topI(),160,20);
				drawText("B: "+bottomIndex+", ImgI: "+botI(),320,20);
			}
			;
			drawImgIndex();
			;
			frame++;
			setTimeout(rendering,400);
		}
		
		function intersects(x,y,u,v,u2,v2) {
			if(x &gt;= u &amp;&amp; x &lt;= u2)
				if(y &gt;= v &amp;&amp; y &lt;= v2)
					return true;
					
			return false;
		}
		
		canvasing.addEventListener('mousedown', function(e) {
			
			var x = e.clientX;
			var y = e.clientY;
			
                        var rect = canvasing.getBoundingClientRect();
			
			x -= rect.left;
			y -= rect.top;

			if(intersects(x,y,ULX,ULY,ULXX,ULYY)) translateRight();
			if(intersects(x,y,URX,URY,URXX,URYY)) translateLeft();
			if(intersects(x,y,LLX,LLY,LLXX,LLYY)) translateDown();
			if(intersects(x,y,LRX,LRY,LRXX,LRYY)) translateUp();
			
		}, false);
		
		rendering();
        </script>
       </td>
      </tr>
     </table>
     <!--End Content Area-->
    </td>
   </tr>
